Notification Action Tracking:
- Mark Done: User completed task from notification -> task_completed_via_notification {channel, task_id}
- Snooze: User snoozed from notification -> notification_snoozed {channel, snooze_duration, task_id}
- Dismiss: User dismissed notification -> notification_dismissed {channel, task_id}
